Note.DepositCount: Number of deposits: back-office points + online banking remittance + personal WeChat recharge
Note.WithdrawalCount: Number of withdrawals: general withdrawal + manual withdrawal
Note.MissionTotal: Total Activity: Promotion Bonus + First Deposit Offer + Deposit Offer + Manual Offer Deposit - Manual Offer Withdrawal
Note.BonusTotal: Divide wealth Manual deposit-bonus manual proposal
Note.Date: Date: From 03:00 on the day of the start time to 03:00 on the next day after the end time. For example, if the start time and end time are both 8/15, the start time is 03:00 on 8/15 to the end time on 8/16 03:00
Note.DifferenTime: System balance settlement time: The system balance settlement time is 03:00 every day, and the balance of the previous day is settled. For example, the balance settlement time of the current day on 8/15 is 8/16 03:00
Note.Differen: System Balance = Today's System Balance - Yesterday's System Balance
Note.Yesterday: Yesterday's system balance includes the account deletion amount
Note.BetCount: The number of bets is the sum of the number of bettors per day, for example, 20 people bet on the 15th, 30 people bet on the 16th, and the sum of the 15th to 16th is 50 people
Note.CashProfitAndLoss: Cash account profit and loss: Yesterday's system balance + online banking remittance + online recharge + Alipay recharge + personal WeChat + background points + other points - general withdrawal - third party withdrawal - manual withdrawal - other withdrawal - today's system balance + unsettled carry-in amount the previous day + unsettled extra income the previous day - unsettled carry-in amount - unsettled extra income
Note.ReportProfitAndLoss: Statement profit and loss: total additional income + general bureau rake + total hand rake - total winnings - total dividends - total activities + deposit fees + withdrawal fees
